Many hospitals are the economy on the mats
This year, most of 000 infections, caused mainly by the incorrect use of antibiotics, were registered in the hospitals.
The conditions hygiene of hospitals, the insufficient number of beds, the overwork of staff medical not help not has block the infections, said the doctor in charge of the center national of the epidemiology.
Many hospitals are also the economy on the mats
It is not long a infection MRSA has been diagnosed to the service of traumatologie of the hospital János.
It bacteria resistant to antibiotics has been detected on a man hospital result has a serious accident.
The patient has been isolated.
