It was subject to a death of means of force.
This teacher british of 54 years in office to the Unity High School of Khartoum in Sudan, was arrested sunday in it and convicted of violation to Islam and of sedition, in accordance of the rule 125 of the rules criminal sudan, to the result of complaints of parents auprés of Ministère of the sudanese education.
