One new festival is the day
As a result of many stories on the creation, by C3 Presents, of a new festival of music to Philadelphia, the promoter -- producer announcement the Vineland Music Festival in New Jersey, in partnership with Festival Republic of the producer british Melvin Benn.
«Pour our company, it is an honor of work with a person who has, no more and no less, inspired the current movement of festivals in Amérique», has given Charlie Jones of C3 to Billboard. com.
C3 product the festival Lollapalooza of Chicago and the Austin City Limits Music Festival.
Vineland, in New Jersey, is a destination summer for the camp-sites.
The festival should be held of 8 on 10 August on a farm privacy of 500 acres to 40 minutes of Philadelphia.
Autrefois known under the name of Mean Fiddler, the director of Festival Republic, Melvin Benn, is one of producers of film festivals the most respected in the world.
In 1989, it has taken the helm of Reading Festival in the United Kingdom, which draws year some 80 000 people.
In 1999, Melvin Benn said the Leeds Festival to its portfolio then, in 2006, Festival Republic has created the Latitude Festival of Henham Park in the Suffolk.
Since 2002, by the copropriétaire, Melvin Benn if is also charged of the production, of the granting of licences and of tasks organisational of Glastonbury Festival, which can now take up 177 500 people.
Qualifiant Glastonbury of «événement the most inspirant» which it has never seen, Charlie Jones of C3 said that his company and that of Melvin Benn work at the same time to give to the region a festival-événement of style european.
«Nous had chosen Philadelphia such as the market and work hard with the Fairmount Parks Commission to create a festival in the town center of Philadelphie», supports Charlie Jones.
«Nous were in talks with the city and the Commission was motivated and classification by the project.
Malheureusement, we we are stuck in of politicailleries to blame the current administration, has Charlie Jones.
«Heureusement, we have been discussing with Melvin Benn and we are we to create a superb festival on a unique site that, ultimement, serve the people of Philadelphia. »
C3 Presents has revived the festival Lollapalooza in 2005 in Grant Park of Chicago, after if be stood in the landscape of festivals in 2002 with the Austin City Limits Music Festival.
Both events have been of revenue the thugs respective of 9.8M$ and of 11.3M$ in.
Both festivals are held in the middle urban.
«Le model european of Melvin Benn is a festival champêtre, and that we have rather place in the areas greens urbains», said Charlie Jones.
The aim is of finance, of a way or of another, the two formulas to give to the time a lot of festival champêtre to the european and urban to the United States. »
Vineland is more or less to halfway between Philadelphia and Atlantic City.
«La community of Vineland, including the mayor, support with enthusiasm the holding of this événement», said Charlie Jones.
The latter refuses of reveal the terms of the agreement, but said «qu'elles are sufficiently interesting to afford to invest in such an event and to a festival that, hope the street, has a long life. »
Charlie Jones said that the ability to host of the festival is «très grande», in the same way that of 80 000 people of Bonnaroo Music Festival in Tennessee.
He says that action has been taken to the groups, but that nothing could not yet be confirmed in time to go in press.
«Vineland will to bite rock, but the music will be there varied, in the hope of attracting all kinds of spectateurs», said Charlie Jones.
Ses partners of C3, which has received the price Top Independent Promoter the last Billboard Touring Awards, are Charlie Walker and Charles Attal.
