" This is not the best thing ", assure the expert.
The Ibex, the index stock spanish, has lost nearly 4% for the 8th november when the index has closed to 15.945.7 points.
Cependant not all the experts have this vision so negative.
Juan Solana, analyst of Intermoney, believes that the Ibex 35 could end the year at 16 points thanks to the reorganization of the portfolios and the traditional contributions to the systems of pensions that are taking place every year during these dates.
Cependant, the expert point that the things are a little different this year he believes that the rallye will place to start of the second week of December, after the bridge of the celebration of the Constitution In particular the 6 December.
The analyst not believe not that the volatility affect the trend of the market.
