The analyst hope that they are positive.
These analysts are of agreement to choose the values which will be the responsibility to lead the Ibex to new cottes maximum.
Mr Solana, of Intermoney, saying that " this year the great values are of return for him ".
The expert included in the portfolio the two major banks and some manufacturers " because when the date approchera, the electrical sector will be very good ".
When, Federico Olucha, of Inversis Banco ensure that the increases will be of to the bank and to the sector industrial.
They constructrices will also benefit of this rallye, in the cases where they are there are.
" ACS for several months recovering of positions we hope that the other constructrices as Ferrovial and FCC suiveront the same way ", is the expert.
The use cyclical will lead in the last part of the year due to the increase of sales in the season of sales of Christmas.
On the other hand, the expert believes that the technological companies will also very well, though in this case it is there not a lot of representation on the spanish market.
Five times in seven years
Durant the past seven years, only in two occasions the months of December has been a month baissier.
The rallye genuine of the end of the year has taken place in 2003, year in which the market share were spent of the crisis caused by the construction of the technological bubble.
This year, in which the Ibex 35 has recovered 28.17 cent, the months of dicembre has recorded an increase of 6.68 cent.
