Congress approved the implementation of the Mifid, which is entry into force the 1 november
Parallèlement to its parliamentary procedure, which has taken end today with the approval of Congress of amendments included in bill in the Senate, the Gouvernement has submitted to a public hearing the regulation which develop the new law, with a view its entry into force before the year end.
The representatives of various groups were agreement to put in particular the efforts made by the members and the senators to negotiate and make the better regulation able to guarantee the protection of investors and of regulate in detail the work of bodies that the markets work effectively.
It Mifid, which changes the Law of the cornerstones of values, means the modernisation of financial markets, when it strengthens the protection of the investors, improve the powers of leaders of the Commission Nationale of the cornerstones of Denominations In particular CNMV) and promote the cooperation between the various leaders of the European Union.
The new rules will of pay of services of consultation financial as well to reasons social specialist that to the people physical or legal and creates a new type of financial services In particular ESIS )- the companies of consultation financial In particular AFI )- that merging the companies of values, the agencies of values and the company managers of portfolio.
In addition, it increases the number of systems for the implementation of operations on the financial instruments, so that it is possible to add to the markets side réglemantés the multilateral systems of negotiation and the systems of internationalisation of orders, which front competition to the current managers of the stock exchange.
The Law must also the companies of services of investment to disclose on the market the information on the key aspects of the profile of case, of exposure to the risk and ways of management of risk and it forces to take a register of all the work that they do, to facilitate the control of the part of the CNMV.
It by the Commission to finance of Congress, several amendments have been added, which a which is in evidence that the debt titularisées will be seen as a financial instrument " complex " view its high risk for the investor, which is is shown with this that it is happened with the debt of companies condition of high risk In particular subprime.
In addition, they have taken of the implementation of the road has taken to define legally the functions that the graduates in Economie can be 30 years when in 1977, has been approved, the royal decree that marked the professional duties reserved for economists.
For its part, the Senate has included the creation of new figures in the financial sector, such as that of the Ombudsman, which work for the benefit of the company, which does not require not the approval of the CNMV and which will give its services of marketing of products and attraction of new customers to various businesses of investment in the same time.
