What assurance would be it.
The car insurance, which covers the driver the face of possible accidents, means a spending important that depend of various factors, such as the age, sex, the age the driver of lead, the civil state, the type of vehicle to ensure or the use that it in fact, among others.
It a car that is the main.
There are only, escoger el seguro of automóvil adecuado es incluso más difícil that elegir el modelo of vehículo.
It is that, choose the insurance car right, is even more difficult that of choose the model of the vehicle.
The car insurance is an agreement between a company of assurance and the insurer.
It be based by a contract of insurance, which states that the company has the value of the premium paid and in return it is responsible of the obligation of pay the compensation in the event of a disaster.
The premium is the price of the insurance, which is established in the light of various factors, such as age, sex, the age the driver of lead, the state civil, the type of vehicle to ensure or the usageque the we in fact, among others.
The companies of insurance companies establish their prices in office of statistics, so that more the likelihood of suffered a crash is high, more the rating to pay is higher.
It is for this reason that the people over the age of 25 and the women must pay premiums more low, as the statistics show that these persones have a rate of accidents more low of to their care.
In the same way, the basis of Censuses, the companies have concluded that the people married have tend to be less of accidents that the drivers employed.
The use as we go along the vehicle impact on the frequency, and therefore on the likelihood of an accident.
En increasing the frequency the chance increase.
They are many the variables that the insurers take into account when establishing the price of the premium.
It is for this, that the driver is well study the situation to choose the car insurance which is basically the best to its profile.
We state here the variables the most important at a time of choosing one or the other kind of assurance, so that it, in addition adapted to the characteristics of the insurer, it offers a reasonable price.
The young people of less of 25 years should be given to various problems when get a contract with a insurance at an accessible price, as can be the little experience in the conduct and the age the driver of lead.
It the right to be well assured is a insurance to any risk, of other options more economic exist.
These drivers the more far-sighted can opt for a insurance any risk with a clear conscience, such a way that they get the security of the insurance to any risk but at a price more accessible.
This form of convention means that the customer pays a part of amount of the disaster.
" The part of the amount of the disaster that the customer pays be established in terms of the value of the premium, which will be higher more the amount will weak ", says Luis Noguera, the head in Spain of First Europa, ombudsman of online insurance.
Another option is the insurance to third enlarged, of the way to what the customer ensure the protection to be given to the damage caused to third parties, but by for those caused on its own car.
In addition, it would cover against the flight, the fires and the loss of the vehicle.
One council.
The reason you are minor of 25 years essaies to be careful and to avoid the claims in the extent of the possible, since this be reflected on the subsidy, can reduce the price of the assurance to the future.
One subsidy is a reduction of tariff of the basis that has the company.
On the contrary, a penalty is a increase of rates of basis.
" These subsidies and the sanctions depend of the company and a profit of it.
The reason the company has been a good year it will be possible to increase the subsidies ", clarifying Noguera.
Beyond this of 25 years it is easier for the drivers to the time of get a contract with a insurance, as the rate of accidents is reduced thanks to the experience gained.
It is for this reason that it is better of choose insurance any risk with a clear conscience.
" Normalement the young people can not not advantage of the experience already gained after an accident ", assure the director of the european company in Spain and added that the majority of accidents take place during the second year of conduct, a time past the ' fear of amateur '.
Cependant, if the customer is married but has not yet of children it is better that it negotiate a insurance to any risk, of momento that its economic situation allows us to do so.
Marriages with children are considered by the insurers as are the people with the rate of accidents the more poor, because the funds are more vulnerable.
In this case the best guarantee would an insurance to any risk with a clear conscience In particular can be of EUR 300 )- or insurance to third enlarged from the third year of life of the vehicle when he has of a high level of subsidy.
" They are going to have a conduct more relaxed and they have a more great purchasing power to allow itself the luxury of take a lot more important of exemptions ", judge Luis Noguera.
Pour the pensioners a insurance to any risk with a clear conscience is better In particular at the same time it of EUR 150 )- or a asurance to third enlarged when the insurer has of a high level of subsidy.
We must say that the car insurance is a thing of importance, not only because it covers the driver the face of possible disasters, but also because it is an important expenditure, that is why it is important to look properly the security that we need the most in our own situation.
