Scientists have previously said that Venus has certainly been a good world to live.
The data result of close european in orbit have shown that the world is certainly twice more small that the world, contrary to what the thought it before.
Venus is the world the most closely of the world.
Both worlds are almost of the same size, with nature similar, even though there are Venus is closer of Sun.
The scientists believe now that we are of billions of years, Venus could have been conditions similar to those of the world, and may even have been habitable.
Let us the greenhouse effect had in dioxide from coal, the erosion air dûe the radiation solar allies to a rotation more slow has led Venus to all a different kind of development.
Aujourd'hui the world is deprived of water, is ravaged by the hurricanes and storms of lightning and has an area of temperature quite hot for there lost the lead.
