In spite of its atmosphere hostile to the life, Venus is more to the world that what we believed Until now, the sunda space union " Venus Express " has found of lightning in the atmosphere and of tourbillons of wind to the poles, such to those that occur in winter on earth.
Depuis almost three decades, the scientists assume that it is of lightning on Venus.
It spot checks union " Venus Express " in has now given the evidence that it has detected of the air electromagnetic to the limit of the atmosphere, the lightning on Venus scandals to a height of about 56 km of cloud in cloud, reports Christopher Russel of the University of California at Los Angeles in the scientific magazine " Nature ".
Selon the well-known theory of the cyprine, the lightning have been seen the life on earth, the storm have encouraged of reactions in the sea which has led to the formation of acidification acids, part of light of the life.
This is not the case on Venus, " The fact life it has been made, it must have been to a date very old of history ", is Sean Solomon of the " Carnegie Institution " to Washington.
It should be made today not of things live to the surface of Venus, the atmosphere is about a hundred times more than on earth, it there sometimes of temperatures of 500 degrees.
" Venus is perhaps the twin-zone circle of the Earth, but it is a twin-zone ", said Russel.
The reason Venus, which is so to the world in volume and aspects, has been hit of a development also different, is the fundamental issue of the mission ESA.
The departure of " Venus Express " in November 2005 was an important step in the research vénusienne, as more no spot checks was under way for the exploration of the world since the 1980s years ten.
The position of researchers, the most recent results of research which have been now presented in several articles of " Nature " does not highlight not only the uniqueness of Venus in the system solar.
