Ainsi the researchers have found, also the tourbillons of wind déja been to the area north, a cold of clouds in south pole, which is still much more quickly.
The phenomenon remind the forces of air in the hemispheres land in winter, wrote a team of researchers around of Giuseppe Piccioni of the Istituto di Astrofisica Spaziale e Fisica Cosmica italian.
The second planéte of sytème solar has almost the same amount that the world is dangerous, with a diameter of 12.100 kilométres, almost as large.
It planéte qualified of star of the evening or the morning turn around the sun in just 225 days.
It is however much more slowly on itself, a day vénusien going 243 days landowners.
It Venus, with temperatures in an area of 460 degrees celsius and a pressure of 92 bar, do not remember not the world, the scientists suspect that the two planétes have formed in conditions similar.
