They Soldats rebels of Manila leave
Dans the Philippines, the rebel soldiers leave, the same that if were entrenched in a hotel in Manila, and which had demanded the withdrawal of the president Gloria Macapagal Arroyo.
The leader Antonio Trillanes, who reprochait to the President the corruption and the electoral fraud, said to the reporters in the hotel that it does not answer any shedding of blood.
The soldiers loyal to power had little before taken to attack the hotel to the aid of gas lacrimogène.
The two dozens of soldiers are were retranchées for hours in the building.
Environ the half of them have been taking place wednesday before the courts in view of an attempt of coup missed in 2003 that among them Trillanes.
It the capacity of the hearing to be away suddenly with about 30 supporters.
The policemen military, which should normally the monitor, had apparently abandoned in favor of it and if were joined to the mutiny.
They are introduced in the hotel Peninsula and demanded the resignation of President Gloria Macapagal Arroyo.
The troops loyal to the power bouclèrent the area around the hotel respectable.
The President convoqua an urgent meeting of Cabinet of security.
The Conseiller national for the security Norberto Gonzales condamna the action of soldiers.
" People in have enough ", said Trillanes.
" We want the people to join us ".
The General Danilo Lim, who control before the unit of the elite of Scouts Rangers, has said that of other units of the army wanted soon join to the way.
The criticism of the regime had called to a strong protest against the President wednesday.
His government is surrounded for months by the accusations of corruption.
The district of finance of Manila was already since 2003 the scene of the attempt of mutiny of about 200 members of the army against Arroyo.
The rising be brisa almost of 24 hours after the refusal of the army of join in.
Since 1986 it have already been held at least seven attempts of coup against the government elected democratically the Philippines.
United the Internet is a key shareholder of Versatel.
United the Internet is is assured a participation of more of 20 per cent of the society of telecommunications Versatel.
The price way by commission is of 14.46 million, as the communiquait the society wednesday.
Seulement 20.05 for cent of capital social would be held.
It was déja speculation earlier on a takeover.
The options remain open to raise even the participation in Versatel.
Avec this step it seeks to accelerate the consolidation of german market of DSL, has given United the Internet.
Just before, assumptions had already been made wednesday to the words of a member, when the bank Berenberg has increased its participation to the operator of network of Düsseldorf of 5 per cent to 15.1 per cent.
The institution of credit has the money only for a third party, tells -t we on the market.
The previous day, United the Internet has already taken a participation of around 10 per cent in the society of mobile phone Drillisch.
In this framework of an increase of capital, Drillisch has placed in the stock exchange 17.4 million new shares to a value of 106.4 millions of euros.
United the Internet in has bought 5.15 millions to 31.1 millions of euros.
In addition, the companies have begun negotiations on cooperation in the field of marketing of products of DSL and mobile phone.
" We renforcons our partnership ", said a spokesman of United the Internet.
Both companies were founded the company in part MSP to to absorb the rival Freenet.
At the moment, the two countries want perhaps met of their participation of ten per cent in Freenet, and do not make use of their right to take 18.49 per cent more in Freenet, told United the Internet thursday.
Both companies are leave but all the options open, but particularly to increase the participation in the S. A. Freenet, has -t we learned.
The negotiations between United the Internet and Freenet where a strategic partnership had made end to the middle.
The poker still hardly predictable on Freenet which lasted for several months is part of the consolidation of german market of telecommunications.
Freenet had at the end of the third quarter 2.9 millions of customers linked by a contract of mobile phone and 1.27 millions of customers DSL and subscriptions complete.
It Holding of United the Internet and Drillisch had so far a direct participation to Freenet of 6.01 per cent.
It has been now agreed that Drillisch bring about four per cent more.
The right to buy the 18.49 for cent of the society of investment Vatas had déja been decided in August.
